<Layout title="About — Agnès Mercadé">
  <section class="about-page">
    <p>
      Born and raised in Barcelona, Spain. I spent three years living in London while studying a
      BA in Photography, an experience that expanded my perspective and continues to influence the
      way I approach creative work.
    </p>
    <p>
      I later returned to Barcelona to complete a Master's degree in Digital Marketing and am now
      based here. I pay close attention to light, composition, and detail, carrying that way of
      looking into everything I do.
    </p>
    <p>
      With a background in photography and digital marketing, my work is shaped by visual thinking
      and intuition. I'm drawn to projects where creativity and strategy connect naturally.
    </p>
    <p>
      Intuition plays an important role in my process, alongside observation and critical thinking.
      Whether working on personal photographic projects, experimental initiatives, or digital
      marketing work, the focus is always on clarity, coherence, and intention.
    </p>
    <p>
      This portfolio brings together both sides of my work and reflects how I approach ideas,
      images, and brands.
    </p>

